# Build Artifacts - Always regenerated by compiler
Debug/
Release/
*.o
*.d
*.elf
*.hex
*.bin
*.list
*.map
*.su
*.cyclo

# IDE User Settings - Personal configurations (do not track)
.vscode/
.idea/
.settings/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Backup and Temporary Files
*.bak
*.backup
*~
*.tmp

# Build Tools Intermediates
*.a
*.lib
*.so
*.dylib
*.obj

# Python (uncomment if using Python tools)
# __pycache__/
# *.py[cod]
# *$py.class
# *.egg-info/

# NOTE: The following ARE tracked (needed for IDE import):
# - .project, .cproject, .mxproject (Eclipse/CubeIDE metadata)
# - *.ioc (CubeMX configuration)
# - *.launch (CubeIDE launch configuration)
# - Core/, Drivers/ (source code and HAL libraries)
# - STM32G474RETX_*.ld (linker scripts)
